Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撲克光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.65,0:00:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:00:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.73,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.50,0:01:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.69,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(遊樂園名產，雞肉薄荷蜜餞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草\N這次的工作好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.67,0:01:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，巡邏真的好好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.81,0:02:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...好好玩\N接下來巡邏哪個好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這次的任務是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.32,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕在咕咕嘟嘟樂園連續發生的\N兒童綁架未遂事件犯人，對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是從剛才看起來\N妳好像只是在玩而已耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有呢，我是在巡邏，巡邏啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇...是咕咕雞耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看！如果是巡邏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該要像那樣\N保護離開父母身邊的小孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護小孩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護小孩不受壞人威脅\N是我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此必須要時常有自製心\N謹慎行動才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且壞人也有很多種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.11,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們會找我們天使隊來\N也是因為事先設想到這種狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而做出使自己的視野\N變狹窄的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在不太能說是上策吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是聽不懂耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.55,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，妳聽懂了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布偶裝巡邏大作戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近發生的多起綁架未遂事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要集中發生在孩子們聚集的\N這個咕咕嘟嘟特區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.61,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，所以才請你們\N重點巡邏這個區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，可是這個廣大的區域\N只靠籠統的巡邏是不夠的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊是啊\N還有好多好玩的東西沒玩到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量把小孩集中在一個地方\N就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們穿上小孩最喜歡的吉祥物\N咕咕雞的布偶裝巡邏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣小孩就會主動的靠過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且穿上布偶裝\N還可以不讓犯人發現地巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好像很有趣，對吧香草？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，這個方法不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N我們會盡快準備好布偶裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有兩個咕咕雞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，還有一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我也要穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬萬不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能讓薄荷．布拉曼修小姐\N做這種事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.91,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個咕咕嘟嘟行星\N是由布拉曼修集團經營的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們怎麼可以這麼失禮的\N讓大小姐穿上布偶裝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不需要介意這些事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.63,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿上這個失禮的布偶裝\N是我們這次的工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能讓您這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩您在這個能夠掌控\N本樂園所有地方的房間監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼，薄荷，妳能看到我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...咕咕雞！兩隻咕咕雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來跟咕咕雞玩吧\N咕咕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個咕咕雞，一動也不動喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！咕咕雞死掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香...香草，怎麼了？\N沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是祈禱的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此啊\N害我白擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大問題？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，布偶裝作戰計劃有個大缺點\N那就是警戒範圍會變得狹窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得這方法已經成功的\N把小孩集中起來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個方法不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好想一想\N這裡有這麼多的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說孩子們不全是為了\N和咕咕雞玩才來這裡的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家是不是都不太聽父母的話\N那裡玩玩，這裡玩玩的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且稍微玩一下就會玩膩\N然後又去玩別的設施，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧\N所以在別的地方也要加強巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.64,0:06:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在小孩很少去的閑靜之處\N發生綁架的可能性非常的高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.48,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾地\N我們必須個別行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.25,0:06:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來，例如...\N梅爾優去植物園，這樣如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.65,0:06:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,植物陰暗處\N是最佳的犯罪地點，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.93,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且雖然說宇宙這麼大\N但是適合穿花偶裝的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想到梅爾優啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是嗎？真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來！大家來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.91,0:06:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家看，這個是食人花\N葉子的直徑竟然有6公尺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是花很可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.12,0:07:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很適合花的裝扮吧\N可愛嗎？可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草則適合在\N最受歡迎的太空世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然得穿上有點\N不可思議的布偶裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這樣也蠻像\N香草的風格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太需要動\N在體力方面也比較輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，還有廣場也需要巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就由剩下的我來穿\N咕咕雞的布偶裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是怎麼可以讓大小姐穿布偶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.88,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了\N你們好像忘了一件重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確，我是布拉曼修家的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.42,0:07:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我也是天使隊的一員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實之前在與此次類似的任務中\N我失去了我重要的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花．法蘭波瓦茲\N以及...佛特．修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天也是因為\N我是布拉曼修家的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒能被派往前線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，只有她們兩人\N沒有對我特別看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對著沮喪的我投以熱切微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著槍林彈雨之中衝去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後兩人並沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.54,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而她們兩人的遺志\N仍然存活在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點，是絕不會消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊的信條是\N所接受的工作一定貫徹到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是為了完成工作\N要我做什麼我都會願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷．布拉曼修\N穿上咕咕雞布偶裝，前去巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.05,0:09:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花樣女孩\N好可愛的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向我吧，梅爾優\N可是有點，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了\N這種溫暖、合身的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然我的眼光是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，犯人出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳...妳說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦，放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我和香草正在追蹤當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，犯人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，雞在說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，薄荷\N妳看，就是那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.56,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下\N請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你們站住沒聽到嗎...\N這次的工作好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們已經無路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說要再繼續玩官兵捉強盜呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.78,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了\N好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔？薄荷心情不錯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前陣子抓到的綁架犯\N好像也偷了園區的布偶裝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.01,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他們本人是否認了\N但是聽說少了一隻公雞布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕，好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個菜單是天然梅爾優的視察勾芡\N不瞞妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是蘋果蛋塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔，我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是香甜好吃的果凍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇...看起來好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？等一下，不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.55,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...又甜又好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我新月的曲線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.59,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.36,0:12:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓它睡著  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.37,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.44,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向魔羯座的你發出\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.69,0:13:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARING  LOVING  YOU

